Story

We come to love not by finding a perfect person, but by learning to see an imperfect person perfectly.

OUR STORY

Fate brought Ngan & Trung together
in the most extraordinary way.
When they recall their first date, every detail aligns perfectly – like lines of code fitting effortlessly. For Trung, it started with a breathless “Wow” at Ngan's intelligence and wit, but as he delved deeper, he found something even more precious – a sincere soul and
a heart full of love.​

​​

It is a love story of two hearts bound
by fate, always lifting each other
through life’s every twist and turn.
Today, the quiet promise Trung once whispered to himself – "I must make this girl my wife" – has blossomed into reality. Hand in hand, they will keep writing
their story, one sweet surprise at a time, filling each day with gentle joy and
endless moments of happiness.

WILL YOU
BE OUR
HONORED GUEST ?

Please respond before May 12, 2025.

​BLESS US
WITH A GIFT

Your presence at our wedding is the greatest gift of all. We feel truly fortunate to be surrounded by such love.

 

Should you wish to honor us with a gift, a contribution to our shared future would be warmly appreciated.

NGUYEN THI
